322	
323	## 10. Accessibility
324	
325	### Semantic Labels
326	
327	| Element | Semantic Label |
328	|---|---|
329	| AppBar | `'Baby Bump home screen, week ${currentWeek}'` |
330	| Mood buttons | `'Feeling ${moodName}, tap to log mood'` |
331	| Checklist chips | `'$itemName, ${isCompleted ? 'completed' : 'not completed'}, double tap to toggle'` |
332	| Quick action buttons | `'$actionName, double tap to $actionDescription'` |
333	| Bottom nav items | Built-in semantics from `NavigationBar` |
334	
335	### Focus Order
336	
337	1. SliverAppBar title/avatar
338	2. Mood emoji buttons (left to right: terrible, bad, okay, good, great)
339	3. Checklist chips (in horizontal scroll order)
340	4. Quick action grid (row 1 left to right, then row 2)
341	5. Weekly tip card
342	6. Bottom navigation items (Home → Browse → Library → Profile)
343	
344	### Contrast Notes
345	
346	- All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 minimum for body, 3:1 for large text)
347	- `lavenderBloom` on white: ratio ~5.2:1
348	- `deepGraphite` on white: ratio ~12:1
349	- `stoneGrey` on white: ratio ~4.7:1
350	- Active bottom nav text uses `lavenderBloom` (5.2:1), inactive uses `stoneGrey` (4.7:1)
351	
352	### Screen Reader Support
353	
354	- `AnnounceRouteChange` for tab switches
355	- `ExcludeSemantics` on decorative elements (fruit emoji, gradient circles)
356	- Live region on mood selection: "Mood logged as ${moodName}"
357	
358	### Touch Target Compliance
359	
360	- All interactive elements minimum 48dp touch target
361	- Mood buttons: 48dp minimum width/height
362	- Checklist chips: 48dp minimum height
363	- Quick action buttons: 48dp minimum, actual 88dp
364	- Bottom nav items: 48dp minimum
365	
366	---
367	
368	## 11. Anti-Patterns
369	
370	**Do Not:**
371	- Add a FAB to Home screen (per UX spec, FAB is None)
372	- Use `SingleChildScrollView` instead of `CustomScrollView` with slivers
373	- Place critical actions below the thumb zone (bottom 1/3 of screen)
374	- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)
375	- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito
376	- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only for content cards)
377	- Use shadows without purpose (only soft diffused shadows on cards)
378	- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp
379	- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text
380	- Display the week banner outside of SliverAppBar context
381	- Skip safe area padding for notch and home indicator devices
382	- Use hard-coded week numbers — derive from `PregnancyProfileProvider.currentWeek`
